{"tid":1644833,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[是他也是你和我]12位素人，12篇訪問，香港人，we stand as one！","createTime":"2019-10-10T16:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T14:08:24.000Z","uid":137959,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e44247d122ca5ac476d01e606c1aa2ebe2498779","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QajVtdD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQajVtdD.jpg&h=3d4b37bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">六月以嚟，你有冇聽過啲難聽過粗口，又或者係啲夭心夭肺嘅說話？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n12位素人分享咗佢哋嘅故事，想同每一個你講，你哋嘅痛，佢哋都承受過。無論親人、路人、政權點傷害我哋，我哋仲有大家！<br />\n香港人，一齊行落去！<br />\n<br />\n「2019年，為每個香港人都烙下了一道又一道的疤痕。除了是肉體上的，也可能是心靈上的創傷。<br />\n<br />\n是次企劃邀請了12位素人分享一句刺痛著自己，又或是警示著自己的說話。團隊把每一個故事，轉化為啟示，讓更多香港人知道，其實你並不孤單，有很多很多的人，承受著同樣的痛，流著同樣的淚。我們還是可以好好走下去，只要我們在一起。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">創而不傷，痛而不蹶。<br />\n香港人，榮光就在前方。 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>&ldquo;A scar means, I survived.&rdquo;</ins></span></strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101636467914044/posts/109110530499971?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101636467914044%2Fposts%2F109110530499971%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5Vlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e06f246e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101636467914044/posts/109110530499971?sfns=mo</a> <br />\n<br />\n企劃專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thehongkongpeople/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthehongkongpeople%2F&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5Vlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=6064fa90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thehongkongpeople/</a>"},{"pid":"09b9e7bcde907be9791ecdc542fda7cdc8073150","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKK2SH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKK2SH8.jpg&h=1d8ace32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>枏, 23, 剛畢業</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「每次出去，我都抱住最大嘅希望，最壞嘅打算。」臉上還帶著點稚氣的枏如是說。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月1日，一群反修例示威者一度佔領立法會大樓，一直有傳警察快將清場，現場氣氛緊張。議事廳內，其中一名示威者拉下了口罩，露出真面目，呼籲大家一同留守：「我哋無得再返轉頭，所以如果你有能力嘅話就佔領呢度；沒能力嘅話你可以用和理非的方式包圍立法會，用你嘅身體保護我們，好嗎？我哋真係冇得再輸。」這名示威者的名字，叫梁繼平。<br />\n<br />\n枏是今次企劃的受訪者中，最年輕的一位，是一名剛畢業不久的大男孩。他說，7月1日晚上，梁繼平的這段宣言深深撼動了他。即使行政長官林鄭月娥於9月4日提出動議撤回修例，枏還是覺得，一切已經太遲了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「如果今次真係輸咗，我哋就真係乜都冇。香港會變成香港市。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「近幾次，我都會同朋友帶裝備出去。有時企埋一邊食煙休息，會有啲aunty叔叔叫我哋小心，同我哋講話『一個都不能少』，話佢哋冇能力走上前，只可以喺後面支持我哋。我覺得好感動。」<br />\n<br />\n枏是一個熱愛時裝的男生。他才剛畢業，還未正式踏進大人的世界，就要背負著很多大人都沒有想過要背負的重擔。「只要自己仲有能力，我都會行出嚟。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n訪問當天，枏穿了一件寬鬆的白T-shirt，配襯著不同的飾物，看得出他對衣著打扮的講究。企劃團隊要求拍下他放聲吶喊的一刻，他起初還有點害羞，要我們陪著他一起大叫。其實，他仍只是個孩子，一個還有夢的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n「慘綠青年<br />\n你比我沒底線<br />\n行裝更多<br />\n年資更淺<br />\n離家更是遠<br />\n竟可以支撐到目前<br />\n誠心祝福你　捱得到　新天地」<br />\n<br />\n《親愛的瑪嘉烈》，是黃耀明為後輩而唱的一首歌。<br />\n慘綠青年，是指那些正值青春年華，理應意氣風發的少年。<br />\n2019年夏，他們應當在戀愛，在追夢，在做盡一切無聊但青春的事。<br />\n他們應當是在陽光下揮汗，而不是在陰霾中灑淚。<br />\n但他們選擇了以寶貴的血肉之軀擋在前方，全因香港已不能再輸。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們誠心祝福，他們會捱得到新天地。.</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cdcb09072d187f37dc61904579629cae1489da0b","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"係度想share多幾個故事比大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以鼓勵到香港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">You are not alone!</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5efa86e4f9aba603c2ae82befd0378ff5f8b8ff8","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z46EaxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ46EaxR.jpg&h=5914fe16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>阿欣, 28, 設計師</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「真係難聽過粗口。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n阿欣是個不擅辭令，總是靜靜觀言察色，愛吃甜品的女生。她從不是個陽光少女，遇到不合理的批評也不懂反擊。 反修例運動開始至今，她經常成為親友揶揄或指責的對象，全因她「好恰」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「你根本就係隨波逐流，人做乜你就做乜。」阿欣的爸爸如是說。<br />\n「你post IG 咪又係為咗攞光環。」她的表姐如是說。<br />\n「唔使成日share新聞，我自己有眼睇。」她的嫂子如是說。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n這些難聽的說話，全都是由阿欣淡然地向企劃團隊複述。她的憤怒與哀傷，總是埋藏於心底裡。彷彿她是個局外人，在訴說別人的事。<br />\n<br />\n但再習慣被攻擊的人，都有感到極度無力的時候。例如是母親歇斯底里的一句「你出去嘅話，我就死俾你睇。」、「你細個好乖，點解會變成咁？」、或是哥哥義正辭嚴的一句「我哋咁錫你，點解你要咁對我哋？」，每一句以愛為名的指責，對阿欣來說，都是一種傷害。<br />\n<br />\n對阿欣來說，自己的家裡就彷如是這個社會的縮影。特首林鄭月娥勸籲大家要「珍惜這個家」，卻未能意識到，自己才是造成家裡撕裂的最大元兇。雖打著愛的旗號，本質上卻是一種權力的宣示，這是不折不扣的情感勒索。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「唔好再用『愛』同『為你好』呢啲字眼，去捆綁其他人嘅自由意志。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n「呢啲說話，以前可能係會傷害到我哋。但依家只會畀到更大嘅力量我哋。我哋會越來越堅強。」近來，阿欣開始學懂在為社會發聲之餘，也為自己發聲。<br />\n<br />\n來到訪問尾聲，她想跟每個在這場運動中受過傷的人說一句：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「你唔係自己一個。我哋好多人都與你同在。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nChoose not to be harmed and you won&rsquo;t feel harmed.<br />\n這句箴言，是出自於羅馬帝國最偉大的君主之一 &mdash; 馬可&middot;奧理略。<br />\n一個人的說話能否真正傷害你，最終決定權還是在你手中。<br />\n無論是不懷好意的謾罵，抑或是經糖衣包裝的「關愛」，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我們或許不能避開，但總能夠一笑置之。只要我們同在一起。</span></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3d3f72f53f44cf6c83d0c817604b9d333925d404","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQybL7o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQybL7o.jpg&h=544c9362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>何潔明, 28, 網店店主</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「幾灰，都要行落去。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n企劃團隊向何潔明發出訪問邀請時，她爽快地一口答應。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: gold;\">「但我諗唔到一句刺痛我嘅說話，因為每一句都只會令我哋更理直氣壯，立場更堅定。」</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「十年前就開始接觸社會運動，然後就到雨傘革命，換來嘅都係一次又一次嘅灰心。但今次，我哋真係退無可退。」她說。<br />\n<br />\n一切皆源於2009年，小明與孖生姐姐何潔泓一次逛街，接過的反高鐵運動文宣單張。驚覺社會原來充斥著不公義的她們，開始活躍於社會運動中，參加苦行、守菜園村，希望盡力為公義發聲。隨著曝光率越來越高，備受注目的她抵受不了壓力，社工系畢業後，便揹起了背包遊歷多個第三世界國家，慢慢淡出了社運界。<br />\n<br />\n雖然退下了火線，小明還是一直在用自己的方法，去關心弱勢社群。流浪了一年，小明回港後開設網店，以「賣一助學一小孩」的形式幫助印度學童。她亦沒有停止關注過香港所發生的大小事，尤其是2017年8月，姐姐被判入獄，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">小明知道她這輩子也不會停止去爭取，那免於恐懼的自由。</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n走遍西藏、尼泊爾、越南、柬埔寨、老撾、泰國、緬甸、印度，她看過世界之大，異國之美，終究卻還是心繫香港。<br />\n<br />\n「點都要行落去。一定要。」<br />\n<br />\n小明的雙臂上佈滿了大大小小，色彩斑斕的紋身，其中一個，是在緬甸紋的，設計最簡約的一個，就那麼短短的兩隻字 &ndash; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><em><em><strong>&ldquo;Stay Strong&rdquo;</strong></em></em></span></span> 。"},{"pid":"94e93f40fb09d8177dbbc78560853e33f0f25352","tid":1644833,"uid":33655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"好真實 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"5c1ab2923dc12f3812cf828c3d9094c3ec8ea39d","tid":1644833,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"［行動post] 一人一個要煲大嘅議題做文宣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekPGjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekPGjS</a>"},{"pid":"e9f72ef7b1e21afa1e718f128a1a009e6fa725eb","tid":1644833,"uid":34332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"推 感動 原來世上都有人同我一樣感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家撐住! 我地都唔係walk alone!"},{"pid":"028c9a56e9eb4ca52c976f09eda404962154d049","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94e93f40fb09d8177dbbc78560853e33f0f25352","tid":1644833,"uid":33655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"好真實 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呀，我地收到故事嘅時候<br />\n有好多都睇到喊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27cc0e76f76bac27859faf835b7614464d02e5f","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9f72ef7b1e21afa1e718f128a1a009e6fa725eb","tid":1644833,"uid":34332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"推 感動 原來世上都有人同我一樣感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家撐住! 我地都唔係walk alone!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"互相勉勵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人唔開心都會收收埋埋<br />\n想比個渠道佢地講出黎"},{"pid":"aa8e82c5985c2ebf283eb6d970a8a2ff2f63316e","tid":1644833,"uid":198350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8613112ac2073511c0735a0122eb90d9fe7b8b57","tid":1644833,"uid":198350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:18:10.000Z","msg":"推again"},{"pid":"48a9a73bccee6cee8bd21d32baa7f0bb92bc3e36","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8613112ac2073511c0735a0122eb90d9fe7b8b57","tid":1644833,"uid":198350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:18:10.000Z","msg":"推again"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"多謝Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9c8d905408733d1b8e8fd28069aedf53d9122b","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3c2f599e45192aa90ba91a0390e6c5eb447bfe","tid":1644833,"uid":34332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7da2a7322d501ddc6cf7aafc902dcb48d72b69e8","tid":1644833,"uid":34332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:16:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf4444009b9ff01e401c1fe22f2b0e64a8c183b0","tid":1644833,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b518be5b098a7f27d48a5bb272cc8b567cbf76e5","tid":1644833,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:49:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5Vlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=5b0bc79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"31da0b91aa38cdd66b2a9131edfdad511eb721c0","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5bb2953af0bd37d91a141a02dd7134c69323e1","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/12/141141_e2d7eacc0eeb46aa4ee5d385b8be23b6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F141141_e2d7eacc0eeb46aa4ee5d385b8be23b6.jpeg&h=1cc42f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Michael, 22, 學生</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「喺我最難過嘅時候，屋企人唔明我。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月9日，民間人權陣線發起反對《逃犯條例》修訂的「反送中」大遊行，六條行車路均被佔據，一直至晚上 10時許，隊尾才抵達立法會總部。晚上11時，主辦方宣佈，遊行人次高達103萬人，創下了1997年以來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n然而，同一個晚上，政府發言人卻宣佈「條例草案於本月12日在立法會恢復二讀辯論」。<br />\n<br />\n汗流浹背地隨著人龍步行了一天的Michael，決定響應網民發起的612佔領行動，於當日把物資送上前線，控訴特區政府漠視民意。6月10日晚上，從來未跟家人討論過政治的他把這個決定告知父母，引發了一段至今仍刺痛著他的對話。<br />\n<br />\n「你呢啲人，俾人洗晒腦！」Michael 的父親冷冷地拋下了這一句，便不發一言回到睡房。<br />\n<br />\n「我爸入咗房後，我就開始同我媽傾。我話我覺得好辛苦，好恐懼，好冇安全感。然後講講下，我忍唔住喊咗出嚟。」眼前這個22歲，六呎高，平日最愛打機的大男孩，痛苦地在母親面前哭了。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n「我爸聽到我喊，衝出嚟鬧我，問我依家過得咁安穩，又唔使我挨窮，有書我讀，我喊咩。我人生第一次，覺得我爸以我為恥，覺得佢好憎我。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「政見唔同，我接受到，亦一直冇期望過佢哋要明白我。但我從來冇諗過會喺屋企人口中聽到呢啲說話。聽到後，我係完全崩潰。」<br />\n<br />\n反修例運動開始之前，Michael的世界很簡單，就只有學業、愛情和打機。跟很多很多愛面子的少年一樣，他已記不起上一次流淚是何時。但6月10日的這個晚上，他哭了，哭得很厲害，哭得一發不可收拾。唯一值得慶幸的是，他堅信自己在做對的事。<br />\n<br />\n親情是一樣很微妙的東西。我們難免會對它有期許，我們難免會希望，它可以無條件地包容自己。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">但即便有天你發現原來親情並非無堅不摧，也請緊記，還有很多很多的同行兒女，在感受著同樣的痛，流著同樣的淚。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em>[url]<span style=\"color: gold;\">為黎明的到來，我們流著淚，但誓不言休。</span>[/url]</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f6516401bfd39a4f687cd76ba2d52da29ae76249","tid":1644833,"uid":137959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRX4y8r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRX4y8r.jpg&h=81a0a5d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f536d91ab4223f707d1fc5eed3425bafc7675bf8","tid":1644833,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c402bb63b64c45bc13eaa31ce283776a51c239","tid":1644833,"uid":94240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}